      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i'll look into a kit. but if it is a nitrogen issue, like something is actually pulling the nutrients out of the soil before the plant can get them, what's the best way to replenish it? i want to make sure the soil stays healthy so this doesn't keep happening.",
